data.description: Delightful 3 bedroom, 2 bath home with 2 car attached garage in desirable Herrin neighborhood! Smaller neighborhood, this home features 1555 sq feet, hardwood floors in living room and dining rooms, mudroom, deep back yard, and deck.  Master bedroom has a full bath with tub/shower combination.  Sheds stay. Roof is 10 years old, newer kitchen appliances, lots of counter space, and several replaced windows.  At under $116 per sq foot, its a great deal! Lot dimensions are 148.5 feet deep by 107 wide. Sellers are motivated, and they have lived here since 2006.
